name: ᒍOᑌᖇᑎEY
description: In the forest between red trees, there is a door. To reach the door, you have to take the steps. Each step you climb up, you will have new experiences. Acceptance and forgiveness will make it easier to reach the door. Once you reach the door, do not hesitate to pass. Also, once you pass the door, there is no way back. When you pass the door, you will meet yourself. The real yourself.  Good luck. // 2021 // ig/samsipahi tw/samsipahi
